reviewText: #FAV ... the mystery of Anna that is :)
I bought this DVD for the Anatasia story.  I was okay.  Of course, they couldn't put all the details of what really happened to the family.

I loved Amy Irving as Anastasia!! The acting by all cast  members including Claire Bloom met my expectations as one good movie. If you like the story of Tsar Nicolai, the last Tsar to rule Russia. Then this is the movie for you! I have always had an intrest in this mystery. I know they said Anna Anderson DNA did not match. However, the remaining family that inherited the money were real quick to dismiss her as Anastasia. They didn't want to believe she was the real McCoy! And let's not mention the money she would have inherited. I felt so sorry for her. Years later, they said they found the graves of young Anastasia and her younger brother. If the other members of the Tsars family were put into acid why were Anastasia and brother buried far away in dirt graves?
Very happy with product.  Had been looking for movie for quite a while. So glad to have found it.  thanks.
great classic.my son loves it and it made an awesome gift! would like to get more classic movies...cant beat some of the classics!!!

What were they thinking? The new adventures is nothing that can be enjoyed by children or adults. The original story is wonderful, but this was such a horrible story with horrible characters, bad acting, and worse puppets. The storyline is unimaginative and tried at worse. We watched it free on demand, and I still feel like I got ripped off. Do not even bother wasting your time.
I loved it on show time on demand, whoever plays pinnochio is brilliant, its a spetaculare, I loved every part, exspecitaly the blue faerie, with a perfect ending. You'll love it too.
I purchased this movie set for the Anastasia movie, and loved it, though not the insanity of Anna Henderson. I think it was well made!
I love Anastasia , it is such a beautiful detailed movie sad , touching , and mysterious.

I absolutely enjoyed the first film, but this feels and looks like a cheap TV movie. The fun scenery and high production values of the 1996 flick are long gone. Instead we get a story that doesn't need to be told, bland and silly characters, cheap puppets and a tiny budget. It boggles my mind that this was a theatrical release anywhere in the world.

Skip it.
Shipping were all great! But i didn't like the movie.
2 discs.  Need I say more? Tacky, cheesy and cheap.  I don't do two movies on one disc, it makes for  horrid viewing.  So this will be returned.
Love this so much great movie
